                        </div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <h3 class="card-title">Website Navigation Systems</h3>
                            <p class="card-description">
                                Intuitive navigation designs with global reach focus, 
                                optimized for user experience and accessibility.
                            </p>
                            <div class="card-tags">
