                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Section -->
        <section class="portfolio-section" id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">
                    Creative problem solver with a passion for beautiful, functional design
                </p>
                
                <div class="about-content">
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <p>
                            Hi, I'm Dharanish, a UI/UX designer specializing in creating responsive, 
                            user-friendly interfaces for web and mobile applications. With expertise 
                            in CSS Flexbox layouts and e-commerce solutions, I bridge the gap between 
                            aesthetics and functionality.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            My approach combines technical precision with creative flair, resulting in 
                            designs that are not only visually stunning but also highly intuitive and 
                            accessible. I have particular experience in textile industry interfaces 
                            and e-commerce platforms, creating solutions that enhance user engagement 
                            and drive conversions.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            When I'm not designing, you can find me exploring the latest web technologies, 
                            contributing to open-source projects, or creating digital art. I'm passionate 
                            about continuous learning and staying at the forefront of design trends and 
                            technologies.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579389083078-4e7018379f7e?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Design Process">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Skills Section -->
